===Noun===
'''oom-pah'''
#{{music}} A [[genre]] of Germanic music (especially Bavarian music) typically involving [[brass]] instruments.
#{{music}} A [[bass]] line characteristic of such music, a bass that alternates lower and higher [[notes]] or [[chords]] on the beat, or that alternates in a mid-high-low-high sequence.

